                     <strong>CLEAN WATER &#61; HAPPY FISH</strong>
            <div class="fishing-line-separator"></div>

                 <p>Poor water quality comes about in many ways – erosion is one, fertiliserrich
run&#45;off and urban stormwater are others. Litter dropped in the street
or at camp sites can make it’s way into our rivers and this makes them
ugly, but also impacts on river life.
</p>
 <p>Please think about this when you’re out on the river especially &#45; take all
your rubbish home, and why not take a spare plastic bag with you and
pick up what some other less thoughtful person might have dropped or
left behind.</p>


